    "solution": "<p>\n  解答：\n</p>\n<p>\n  \\[\n  U_m = \\sqrt{2} \\times 220 = 311\\,V\n  \\]\n  \\[\n  U_d = \\frac{U_m}{2\\pi}(1 + \\cos \\alpha)\n  = \\frac{311}{2\\pi}(1 + 0.866)\n  = 92.3\\,V\n  \\]\n  \\[\n  I_d = \\frac{U_d}{R_d} = \\frac{92.3}{20} = 4.615\\,A\n  \\]\n  \\[\n  \\boxed{U_d = 92.3\\,V} \\quad \\boxed{I_d = 4.615\\,A}\n  \\]\n</p>"
